OL,3,CAnalysis: Autumn tax rises loom as
OL,4,Cgovernment borrowing rises in June
OL,6,FCapital Economics warns that the
OL,7,Fgovernment's failure to deliver
OL,8,Fplanned welfare cuts - and its
OL,9,Fassumption that borrowing will
OL,10,Fcontinue to overshoot - means the
OL,11,Fchancellor will need to find #15`25
OL,12,Fbillion in the Autumn Budget.
OL,14,F"We doubt the gilt market will
OL,15,Ftolerate a significant increase in
OL,16,Fborrowing," Alex Kerr said.
OL,18,F"She will probably have to raise taxes
OL,19,Finstead."
