OL,3,CAnalysis: Autumn tax rises loom as
OL,4,Cgovernment borrowing rises in June
OL,6,F"We are committed to tough fiscal
OL,7,Frules, so we do not borrow for day-to-
OL,8,Fday spending and get debt down as a
OL,9,Fshare of our economy," said Darren
OL,10,FJones, Chief Secretary to the
OL,11,FTreasury, in response to the June
OL,12,Fnumbers.
OL,14,F"This commitment to economic stability
OL,15,Fmeans we can get on with investing in
OL,16,FBritain's renewal."
